Histopathological analysis of experimental liver tissues following administration of 
   T. bellirica fruit extracts and ellagic acid (EA) in diclofenac (DCF) treated rats. 
   A- Control rats; 
   B- DCF treated rats; 
   C- DCF + silymarin treated rats; 
   D- DCF + EA treated rats; 
   E- DCF + aqueous extract-treated rats; 
   F- DCF + ethyl acetate extract treated rats. The blue color arrow represents central vain; black arrow represents the nucleus, and the yellow arrow represents inflammatory cells.
